{"tid":1288132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將晤張建宗　黃碧雲：倡下星期復開財委會　二樓會議室運作正常","createTime":"2019-07-05T13:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T14:00:56.000Z","uid":63865,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f8fccc75bfe8cbfdc47a8992dc8f9b2ebf4e7a13","tid":1288132,"uid":63865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:21:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/將晤張建宗-黃碧雲-倡下星期復開財委會-二樓會議室運作正常/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B0%87%E6%99%A4%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E9%BB%83%E7%A2%A7%E9%9B%B2-%E5%80%A1%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%A9%E9%96%8B%E8%B2%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E4%BA%8C%E6%A8%93%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%AE%A4%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%2F&d=TgwWsw16K2C65RuBgL3vHRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=300ffca2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B0%87%E6%99%A4%E5%BC%B5%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%97-%E9%BB%83%E7%A2%A7%E9%9B%B2-%E5%80%A1%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%A9%E9%96%8B%E8%B2%A1%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83-%E4%BA%8C%E6%A8%93%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%AE%A4%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%2F&h=e0c7398d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/將晤張建宗-黃碧雲-倡下星期復開財委會-二樓會議室運作正常/</a>"},{"pid":"555ae54c3f237f05a5d34e86034f202da9f7bbac","tid":1288132,"uid":63865,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"民主派議員今日（5日）下午將與政務司司長張建宗會面，商討財委會會議的安排等事宜。會面前民主黨及公民黨的立法會議員均表示，立法會大樓內部分會議室運作正常，認為財委會部分會議可在大樓內進行，無須以書面傳閱方式表決撥款，將要求下周重開財委會會議。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員黃碧雲表示，大樓內二樓 2A 及 2B 會議室運作正常 ，不論點票系統、議員座位上的8屏幕以及投影機，都沒有受損，運作正常；只是傳召議員投票的響鐘設施未能運作。<br />\n<br />\n黃碧雲指該會議室可容納全體70名議員，並指民主黨認為可在大樓內進行財委會會議，優先處理和民生有關的撥款，減少對市民的影響，民主黨將要求下周重開財委會會議。"},{"pid":"fbab46637fdfc511928b932f07dca87f78176eea","tid":1288132,"uid":55941,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黃碧雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f43d3040a43772c76627b4275615c47c785a267","tid":1288132,"uid":63865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:24:11.000Z","msg":"她又指會在和張建宗的會面中， 表達政府應該為今次《逃犯條例》修訂的政治危機負責，林鄭月娥應該下台，社會才能重新出發。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪：不應開書面傳閱  轉地方開會先例<br />\n<br />\n公民黨立法會議員譚文豪亦表示，2 號會議室早前已提升部份設施，即使部分設施未能提供服務，就算人手點票亦可以。他舉例舊立法會大樓的設施，可能不及現時大樓先進，甚至英國國會亦是以人手點票。他表示，最重要的是不應開書面傳閱或到其他地方開會的先例，以免日後面對具爭議議題時，政府及建制派會重施故技。"},{"pid":"22fccd084226566125d5087e868299fed7a4d14e","tid":1288132,"uid":63865,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:25:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老母黃碧雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2a18cc35cb0205b8f9d469b2c2abd6a5ec3d6b","tid":1288132,"uid":63865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"未撚傾掂數就見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見乜撚"},{"pid":"3334d1980709ecc401f424fe4873051d0b2beba5","tid":1288132,"uid":38991,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"樓主遲左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次再開post啦"},{"pid":"64037feeada16de60d759854eacbb0c545fc6510","tid":1288132,"uid":84068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:31:09.000Z","msg":"........點解冇人屌醒佢"},{"pid":"b960df47c6054f129acd28c011c393501378a2b6","tid":1288132,"uid":263161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:31:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc06810a1ac216451447f4fc268c7420be5e0be4","tid":1288132,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:34:51.000Z","msg":"豬西隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e5f63075f06848d5743f779eacd18a164fb36f","tid":1288132,"uid":222140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T13:35:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"